description:
‘Second Coming’ continues! Bastion’s forces attack – and X-Men begin to die! The net draws in around Cable and Hope – is this the final hour for mutantkind?

Includes material reprinted from X-Men Legacy #235, X-Force #26 and Uncanny X-Men #524.

Manga Contents

  • Tough: Ryū o Tsugu Otoko Ch. 20
  • Play Masonry Ch. 8
  • SASHIKO + 48GROUP 4-koma Gekijō Yonpachi+ Ch. 203

The ‘Second Coming’ saga continues! Hope has reached Utopia, but is it a safe haven – or a deadly prison? Bastion closes the jaws on his trap, and the X-Men face total annihilation!

Includes material reprinted from New Mutants #13, X-Men: Legacy #236 and X-Force #27.

San Francisco has become an inescapable prison for all mutants – and Bastion intends to wipe them out! Wolverine leads X-Force on a suicide mission into the future! The X-Men face total annihilation in ‘Second Coming’!

Includes material reprinted from Uncanny X-Men #525, New Mutants #14 and X-Men: Legacy #237.

Acclaimed writer/artist John Byrne takes the web-slinger's reigns and reinvents the Spider-Man mythos for the 21st century! Witness your favorite web-spinner's earliest adventures as he faces off - for the first time - against the likes of Dr. Octopus, the Vulture, Sandman, the Green Goblin, the Lizard, Mysterio and Electro! Guest-starring Spidey's supporting cast, the Fantastic Four and heroes from throughout the Marvel Universe, in a decidedly different take on Spider-Man's formative years! Collecting SPIDER-MAN: CHAPTER ONE #0-12.
name: TPB

description:
Waitresses, arms dealers, human traffickers, pregnant crime lords, bad dreams and feral female fighters can't stop Wolverine from carving his way to victory in this razor-sharp series reboot by acclaimed novelist and comics scribe Greg Rucka (Whiteout, Queen & Country). And see Logan do what he does best against his archenemy, Sabretooth!

Plus: the unsettling threats of Cry and Vapor! Guest-starring Nightcrawler!

Collecting WOLVERINE (2003) #1-19.
name: Wolverine by Greg Rucka Ultimate Collection
